// the private IP address and allocation method, whether it is the primary
// configuration, and typed references to the subnet, public IP address, and
// application security groups. Select by the configuration's Azure resource ID.
private azure.subscription.networkService.interface.ipConfiguration @defaults("name privateIpAddress primary") {
