// Azure Lighthouse authorization
//
// A single grant within a registration definition, pairing a managedBy-tenant
// principal with the built-in role it receives on the delegated scope. The
// `principalId` and `principalIdDisplayName` fields identify the user, group,
// or service principal; `roleDefinition` resolves the granted role; and
// `delegatedRoleDefinitionIds` is populated when the role is User Access
